STATE
v.
Michael Anthony ELLIOTT. No. 716P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 26, 2006. Daniel P. O'Brien, Assistant Attorney General, Michael Nifong, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 22nd day of December 2005 by Defendant for "Notice of Appeal":

"Motion Dismissed ex mero motu by order of the Court in conference this the 26th day of January 2006."
